import React from 'react'
import {
    AppBar,
    Toolbar,
    ListItem,
    IconButton,
    ListItemText,
    Avatar,
    Divider,
    List,
    Typography,
    Box
} from "@material-ui/core"
import {
    ArrowBack,
    AssignmentInd,
    Home,
    Apps,
    ContactMail
} from "@material-ui/icons"

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <Box component="nav">
          <AppBar position="static" style={{background: "#111"}}>
              <Toolbar>
                <IconButton>
                  <ArrowBack style={{color: "#4E538F"}}/>
                </IconButton>
              </Toolbar>
            </AppBar>  
        </Box>
    )
}

export default Navbar
